<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend Framework should send special header X-Powered-By with value "Zend Framework " as a signature "This application uses ZF". Similary function offers Nette framework. This can be used for analizing how much sites use ZF, which version etc.</p>

